"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"即将推出：存储在可交易 NFT 中的 ERC-20 代币。\\n具体做法： WOOL Pouches，每个人可以燃烧1万羊毛，获取一个农民。\\n\\n每个羊毛包，会给出一个有限的羊毛供应。剩下的4年解锁。你可以把解锁的wool收获，也可以把带着wool的羊毛包进行交易。\\n\\n Pouches会四年解锁，解锁期间可以进行交易 \\n\\n重点玩法段落原文：\\n\\nThus far, I have shown you: NFTs that steal other NFTs; NFTs that tax other NFTs; and NFTs that shakedown other NFTs. Introducing my next offering: ERC-20 tokens that are stored within tradable NFTs. I call them WOOL Pouches. Here is how they work:\\n\\nEvery WOOL Pouch starts with a finite WOOL supply. The first 10,000 WOOL are immediately accessible to the minter. This gives everyone a chance to burn 10,000 WOOL in exchange for a Farmer.\\n\\nThen, the remaining WOOL in the Pouch unlocks at a constant rate over 4 years. You may claim any unlocked WOOL or trade your Pouch including the WOOL inside at anytime.\\n\\n**原文翻译**\\n我的职责不仅是确保您的代币得到即时和安全的救援，而且还要保护我们宝贵的 $WOOL 的长期健康。\\n\\nWOOL 是游戏最宝贵的资源和治理代币。玩家花费、赌注、保存和燃烧 WOOL。\\n\\n最初，我打算通过燃烧 18 亿只羊毛，将 40,000 头 Gen 1 Sheep & Wolves 带入农场。相反，只召唤了3809只。 Gen 1 Sheep & Wolves 变得更加稀有，但这留下了额外的 17 亿羊毛可用。\\n\\n只有 76M WOOL 被烧毁。远低于预期的1.8B。行动是必要的，我将利用合理的代币经济学来维护游戏的完整性，保护所有的羊和狼，并确保您的 WOOL 安全。我还必须确保农民的公平分配。\\n\\n到目前为止，我已经向你展示了：窃取其他 NFT 的 NFT；对其他 NFT 征税的 NFT；和影响其他 NFT 的 NFT。介绍我的下一个产品：存储在可交易 NFT 中的 ERC-20 代币。我称它们为羊毛袋。以下是它们的工作原理：\\n\\n每个 WOOL Pouch 都从有限的 WOOL 供应开始。铸币厂可立即获得前 10,000 件羊毛。这让每个人都有机会燃烧 10,000 WOOL 以换取农民。\\n\\n然后，小袋中剩余的 WOOL 会在 4 年内以恒定速度解锁。您可以随时索取任何未锁定的 WOOL 或交易您的邮袋，包括里面的 WOOL。\\n\\n我的 WOOL Pouch 和你的一样。我坚持自己的标准，我们都遵守相同的规则。\\n\\n您的 WOOL Pouch 会有多丰富？羊：这取决于你喜欢冒险的程度。狼队：高枕无忧。你会喜欢游戏的这一章。\\n\\n明天，我将发布本章的更多细节，向您介绍我们的审核员，并分享拯救绵羊和狼的时间表。\\n\\n**原文：**\\n\\nMy duty is not only to ensure the immediate and safe rescue of your tokens, but also to protect the long-term health of our precious [$WOOL](https://twitter.com/search?q=%24WOOL&src=cashtag_click).\\n\\nWOOL is the most precious resource and governance token of the game. Players spend, stake, save, and burn WOOL.\\n\\nIn the earliest days, I had intended to bring 40,000 Gen 1 Sheep & Wolves onto the farm, through burning 1.8 billion WOOL. Instead, only 3,809 were summoned. Gen 1 Sheep & Wolves became far more rare, but this left an extra 1.7 billion WOOL available.\\n\\nOnly 76M WOOL was burned. Far less than the 1.8B expected. Action is necessary, and I will leverage sensible tokenomics to maintain the game's integrity, protect all Sheep & Wolves, and keep your WOOL safe. I must also ensure fair distribution of Farmers. \\n\\n \\n Thus far, I have shown you: NFTs that steal other NFTs; NFTs that tax other NFTs; and NFTs that shakedown other NFTs. Introducing my next offering: ERC-20 tokens that are stored within tradable NFTs. I call them WOOL Pouches. Here is how they work:\\n\\nEvery WOOL Pouch starts with a finite WOOL supply. The first 10,000 WOOL are immediately accessible to the minter. This gives everyone a chance to burn 10,000 WOOL in exchange for a Farmer. \\n\\nThen, the remaining WOOL in the Pouch unlocks at a constant rate over 4 years. You may claim any unlocked WOOL or trade your Pouch including the WOOL inside at anytime.\\n\\nMy WOOL Pouch works the exact same way as yours. I hold myself to the same standards, and we are all playing by the same rules.\\n\\nHow bountiful will your WOOL Pouch be? Sheep: that will depend on how much you like risk. Wolves: sit back and relax. You will love this chapter of the game.\\n\\nTomorrow, I will release more details of this chapter, introduce you to our auditor, and share the timeline for rescuing Sheep & Wolves.\",\"timestamp\":1637823992,\"title\":\"wolfgameV2 第二次更新预告篇\"},\"digest\":\"nwMFt-3Eo8WpjanmO3bnLkw3F5DD2umzE8w6C_ayawI\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x41A2F513BB1433d306da5DE5a537CCa75ec9e073\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"L214i0h_PpGKXCG1dOF22b8gzpa7nOfdWts6z2Z1sfo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"OFkSNSHnYepTdQkY8fXmc3Hj6gXbChhxQ0OMs-3b7hI\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"yQEmbQvaRpaBJMUnxPI_jzM